@loicmathieu

Should the title be Authorization of Web Endpoints using configuration ? As securing Web Endpoints is also possible (partialy) using annotation ?

The plan is for this document to have all the information related to all types of the authorization, configuration and annotation based, and whatever else we may come up with, if it is not in this document then it will be added later I suppose. This PR is only about turning security.adoc into a front end Security page by pushing some of the current content into the new documents

